ie sowie Richtlinie Schiedsverfahren bei DBA-Konflikten.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 4aAußensteuerrecht. 4aBEPS. 4aEuropäisches Steuerrecht. 4aUnionsrecht. 4adirekte/indirekte Steuer. 7aLAW / International.2bisacsh1 aDobratz, Lars, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aEnglisch, Joachim, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aFehling, Daniel, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aFlüchter, Karsten, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKofler, Georg, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aOellerich, Ingo, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aReimer, Ekkehart, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aSchaumburg, Harald, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2z978311069629508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Law 2019z9783110606249oZDB-23-DGC40uhttps://doi.org/10.9785/978350438604740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783504386047423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783504386047.jpg  a978-3-11-069629-5  DG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2b2020  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGCb2019  aZDB-23-DGGb2019